('loop in', 'To include someone in a conversation or email thread', 'Meeting & Email Phrases', 'Please loop in the DevOps team when you reply so they''re aware of the change.', 'B1'),
('touch base', 'To make brief contact with someone to check in or share updates', 'Meeting & Email Phrases', 'Can we touch base tomorrow morning before the client call?', 'B1'),
('moving forward', 'From this point on; used to signal a change in approach or process', 'Meeting & Email Phrases', 'Moving forward, all code changes must go through a pull request review.', 'B1'),
